  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate scintigraphic methods as objective factors for
      functional outcome in patients treated with ileal-pouch-anal anastomosis (IPAA). The
      gastrointestinal transit-time and the degree of evacuation are evaluated in relation to the
      functional outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
